# Claude Code Project Instructions

## Effect Patterns

This project uses Effect-TS. Effect patterns are installed as Claude Code skills
under `.claude/skills/`. Claude Code loads each skill on demand – the full content
is only pulled into context when the skill's description matches the task, so there
is no eager-loading cost.

Install the recommended starter set:
```bash
npx effect-claude-primitives --starter
```

List every available skill, or install a specific subset:
```bash
npx effect-claude-primitives --list
npx effect-claude-primitives --skills effect-core-concepts,effect-error-handling,effect-testing
```

